# Popup and Modal Size Standards

- For all future popup/modal dialogs, use one unified size across the whole site.
- Unified modal size (mandatory unless user requests exception):
  - `width: min(1280px, 98vw)`
  - `max-height: 96vh`
- Do not create smaller popup variants for specific pages unless the user explicitly asks.
- All popup cards must support vertical scrolling when content is long (`overflow: auto`).
- Keep headers sticky when possible for long forms, so title/actions remain visible.
- Do not use one-off inline width styles for modals unless explicitly requested by user.
- Reuse shared modal classes (for example `details-card` + size modifier classes) to keep behavior consistent across current and future popups.
